ğŸ“š Book Recommendation System
A content-based recommendation system that suggests books based on user input. It uses TF-IDF vectorization and cosine similarity to recommend titles based on book descriptions (titles + authors).

ğŸ” Project Overview
This project analyzes a dataset of 11,000+ books and builds a recommendation engine that:
Explores rating distributions and author contributions.
Uses NLP techniques to vectorize book metadata.
Suggests similar books based on a user-provided title.

ğŸ§  Techniques Used
TF-IDF Vectorization (title + author combined)
Cosine Similarity for recommendation
Plotly for interactive visualizations

ğŸ“Š Exploratory Data Analysis
